Start
/ Compress + decompress through PLang must round-trip the wrapped value losslessly.
/ Verifies coverage row 3.9 — the developer-facing surface for Stage 3's flat Compress.
- set %original% = 'The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.', type=text/plain
- compress %original%, write to %archived%
- assert %archived!Type% equals 'archived'
- decompress %archived%, write to %restored%
- assert %restored% equals 'The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.'
